Simphiwe Ngema Reveals that she&#8217;s pregnant with Dumi Masilela&#8217;s Baby The widow of Dumi Masila is overwhelmed with emotions and the events in her life right now. Last week she attended her husband&#8217;s memorial service at Kempton Park and she couldn&#8217;t stop crying. She sat there like she couldn&#8217;t wait to hear someone say &#8220;Dumi is okay guys go home, this was just a bad joke &#8220;. Simphiwe was seen crying and forcing a smile everytime a beautiful memory of her husband was shared. She braved through the service but collapsed towards the end. She was immediately rushed to a near by hospital where tests were ran and she was told she&#8217;s 10 weeks pregnant.